             <p>Stupko, Turovsky, Filippenko 2007, 190 Vinogradov D.Feissel</p>
             <p>Bosporos Grégoire 1929, № 9 (Cyzicus, IV century C.E.)</p>
             <p/>
             <p>Stupko, Turovsky, Filippenko 2007</p>
